WEBVTT

00:03.003 --> 00:04.772
[ SOUNDS OF DIGGING ]

00:04.772 --> 00:07.475
[ GRUNTING ]

00:10.244 --> 00:12.346
[ INDISTINCT CHATTER ]

00:12.346 --> 00:14.415
[ THUNDER CRACKLING ]

00:17.685 --> 00:18.152
>> COME ON, MAN.

00:18.152 --> 00:20.121
HURRY UP.

00:20.121 --> 00:22.490
>> IF YOU IN SUCH A HURRY,

00:22.490 --> 00:24.492
YOU COULD HELP.

00:26.494 --> 00:28.329
[ THUNDER RUMBLING ]

00:28.329 --> 00:29.530
DON'T TELL ME,

00:29.530 --> 00:31.365
YOU SCARED OF THAT THING.

00:31.365 --> 00:32.031
>> YOU HEARD THE STORIES,

00:32.031 --> 00:33.467
YOU KNOW THE LEGENDS.

00:33.467 --> 00:36.003
>> MAN, THAT'S ALL THEY IS--

00:36.003 --> 00:38.106
STORIES.

00:38.106 --> 00:38.572
>> AREN'T WE DIGGIN'

00:38.572 --> 00:39.940
BASED ON STORIES?

00:39.940 --> 00:41.975
>> YEAH, BUT STORIES OF GOLD

00:41.975 --> 00:43.444
AND FAMILY HEIRLOOMS IS MUCH

00:43.444 --> 00:45.979
MORE BELIEVABLE OVER MONSTERS

00:45.979 --> 00:48.349
AND LIVING SCARECROWS.

00:49.750 --> 00:53.321
[ MUSIC ]

00:54.355 --> 00:56.724
[ THUNDER RUMBLING ]

00:56.724 --> 00:59.227
MAN, GET OFF ME.

01:03.497 --> 01:05.866
[ LAUGHING ]

01:07.501 --> 01:09.270
MAN, LEAVE OFF THAT THING.

01:09.270 --> 01:11.672
COME AND HELP ME.

01:13.040 --> 01:28.289
[ MUSIC ]

01:33.994 --> 01:35.929
[ SNARLING ]

01:35.929 --> 01:37.498
[ GAGGING ]

01:37.498 --> 01:39.300
WHAT WAS THAT, OL' JEFFERS?

01:39.300 --> 01:41.635
YOU GONNA FINALLY HELP?

01:45.606 --> 01:46.407
YOU, SIR,

01:46.407 --> 01:47.608
ARE STARTIN' TO ANNOY--

01:47.608 --> 01:49.310
[ SNARLING ]

