36:34.660 --> 36:35.261
HOLY CRAP!

36:35.261 --> 36:37.162
OH GOD!

36:38.930 --> 36:39.831
WYATT?

36:39.831 --> 36:41.567
WYATT, IS THAT YOU, MAN?

36:41.567 --> 36:42.368
THIS IS NO TIME TO BE MESSIN'

36:42.368 --> 36:44.270
AROUND WITH ME, WYATT.

36:44.270 --> 36:45.637
YOU OUT THERE?

36:45.637 --> 36:47.706
[ YELPING ]

36:50.709 --> 36:52.844
[ SCREAMING ]

36:52.844 --> 36:55.781
OH MY GOD, OH MY GOD.

36:55.781 --> 36:57.816
[ WHIMPERING ]

37:00.419 --> 37:01.453
DAMN IT, WYATT!

37:01.453 --> 37:02.721
WHAT ARE YOU DOIN', MAN?

37:02.721 --> 37:03.289
TRYIN' TO SCARE THE PISS

37:03.289 --> 37:04.423
OUT OF ME, MAN?

37:04.423 --> 37:05.857
WALKIN' AROUND IN THESE WOODS.

37:05.857 --> 37:07.693
CAN WE JUST GET THE KIDS?

37:07.693 --> 37:08.093
GOD--

37:08.093 --> 37:08.860
[ GROWLING ]

37:08.860 --> 37:09.995
OH.

37:09.995 --> 37:10.962
OH YOU'RE GETTIN' INTO

37:10.962 --> 37:13.064
CHARACTER, I SEE, OKAY.

37:13.064 --> 37:15.367
SAVE IT FOR THEM, MAN.

37:15.367 --> 37:16.034
[ GROWLING ]

37:16.034 --> 37:16.635
HEY!

37:16.635 --> 37:19.137
COME ON!

37:19.137 --> 37:25.311
[ MUSIC ]

37:25.311 --> 37:27.446
[ GROWLING ]

37:29.515 --> 37:31.082
>> IT'S YOUR TURN.

37:31.082 --> 37:33.084
DO JAMES EARL JONES.

37:33.084 --> 37:33.785
[ CHUCKLING ]

37:33.785 --> 37:34.420
>> ALL RIGHT.

37:34.420 --> 37:35.521
SIMBA, YOU DELIBERATELY

37:35.521 --> 37:36.988
DISOBEYED ME.

37:36.988 --> 37:37.589
EVERYTHING THE LIGHT

37:37.589 --> 37:38.590
TOUCHES IS OUR KINGDOM--

37:38.590 --> 37:42.027
[ ANIMAL HOWLING ]

37:42.027 --> 37:44.062
>> THIS ISN'T FUN ANYMORE.

37:44.062 --> 37:46.097
>> STOP BEING SUCH A BABY.

37:46.097 --> 37:47.132
>> I DUNNO, BEC.

37:47.132 --> 37:47.999
THOSE GUYS AT THE BAR

37:47.999 --> 37:50.235
CREEPED ME OUT, TOO.

37:50.235 --> 37:51.837
>> CAN YOU HELP ME OUT HERE?

37:51.837 --> 37:53.505
>> I MEAN, IT'S A LITTLE CREEPY,

37:53.505 --> 37:55.240
BUT IT'S FUN, THOUGH.

37:55.240 --> 37:57.008
>> IT'S NOT FUN ANYMORE.

37:57.008 --> 37:57.843
>> COME ON, MAN, LIKE,

37:57.843 --> 37:59.345
AN EVIL SCARECROW?

37:59.345 --> 38:00.245
LIKE, I'D BE MORE CREEPED OUT

38:00.245 --> 38:01.246
ABOUT FUTURE PEDOPHILES

38:01.246 --> 38:02.981
OF AMERICA...

38:02.981 --> 38:03.915
AT THE BAR.

38:03.915 --> 38:04.383
>> RIGHT?

38:04.383 --> 38:05.250
THAT'S WHAT I'M SAYIN'.

38:05.250 --> 38:06.352
IF MISS HUMPS-LOT OVER HERE

38:06.352 --> 38:06.952
DIDN'T FLIRT WITH THEM THE WHOLE

38:06.952 --> 38:09.621
TIME, GETTIN' 'EM ALL RILED UP.

38:09.621 --> 38:11.256
>> WHATEVER.

38:11.256 --> 38:13.425
>> YOU WERE REALLY FLIRTY.

38:13.425 --> 38:14.860
>> WHORISH.

38:14.860 --> 38:17.363
[ INDISTINCT CHATTER ]

38:17.363 --> 38:19.097
[ STICKS CRACKING ]

38:19.097 --> 38:20.065
>> WHO THE FUCK IS OUT THERE?!

38:20.065 --> 38:21.199
I'LL KICK YOUR ASS!

38:21.199 --> 38:21.833
>> SIT YOUR ASS DOWN!

38:21.833 --> 38:22.468
WHAT THE FUCK DO YOU THINK

38:22.468 --> 38:24.069
YOU'RE DOING?

38:24.069 --> 38:25.003
>> I MEAN, YOU DON'T WANT 'EM

38:25.003 --> 38:26.372
TO KNOW WHERE WE ARE.

38:26.372 --> 38:26.938
>> YEAH, LIKE THEY CAN'T SEE

38:26.938 --> 38:27.973
THAT IN THE FUCKIN' DARK.

38:27.973 --> 38:28.840
>> FUCK OFF.

38:28.840 --> 38:30.376
>> CAN WE PLEASE GO HOME?

38:30.376 --> 38:31.109
>> ALL RIGHT, COME ON,

38:31.109 --> 38:32.177
COME ON, CALM DOWN.

38:32.177 --> 38:33.011
MAYBE REBECCA WAS RIGHT.

38:33.011 --> 38:33.845
MAYBE WE SHOULD JUST STEP AWAY

38:33.845 --> 38:34.546
FROM THE FIRE

38:34.546 --> 38:36.582
AND SEE WHAT HAPPENS.

38:40.819 --> 38:41.853
[ CHUCKLING ]

38:41.853 --> 38:42.788
>> OH YEAH.

38:42.788 --> 38:44.590
I GOT THIS.

38:44.590 --> 38:45.824
>> OH MY GOD.

38:45.824 --> 38:47.292
ANGER MANAGEMENT CLASSES

38:47.292 --> 38:49.127
HAVE DONE WONDERS FOR YOU.

38:49.127 --> 38:50.929
>> WHO BETTER TO PROTECT US?

38:52.564 --> 38:54.766
>> NO, HE STAYS WITH ME!

38:58.737 --> 38:59.405
>> YEAH, LET'S GO

38:59.405 --> 39:01.940
GET US A SCARECROW.

39:01.940 --> 39:03.742
OR A REDNECK.

39:03.742 --> 39:05.844
WHATEVER.

39:05.844 --> 39:06.311
>> NO.

39:06.311 --> 39:06.978
>> OH, LET'S GO GET US A

39:06.978 --> 39:07.713
SCARECROW, OR A REDNECK,

39:07.713 --> 39:08.179
WHATEVER-- NO!

39:08.179 --> 39:08.914
I JUST WANNA FUCKIN' SIT HERE

39:08.914 --> 39:11.049
AND DRINK MY GODDAMN BEER.

39:11.049 --> 39:11.517
>> LET'S GO!

39:11.517 --> 39:13.652
>> NOPE, NOPE.

39:17.188 --> 39:19.057
>> LET'S GO!

39:30.068 --> 39:34.773
[ MUSIC ]

39:34.773 --> 39:37.175
>> DAGNABBIT, VIRG!

39:37.175 --> 39:39.144
WHAT HAVE YOU GOTTEN US INTO?

39:42.481 --> 39:44.750
I HATE YOU.

39:51.890 --> 39:54.059
OH, SHIT.

39:54.059 --> 39:55.961
IT'S THEM KIDS.

39:55.961 --> 39:58.096
WHAT DO I DO NOW?

40:03.101 --> 40:04.470
>> DO YOU SEE-- DO YOU--

40:04.470 --> 40:06.037
>> WHAT THE FUCK IS THAT?

40:06.037 --> 40:06.972
>> OKAY, SHH!

40:06.972 --> 40:07.405
>> DID YOU SEE?

40:07.405 --> 40:09.608
>> OKAY.

40:09.608 --> 40:10.141
>> FUCK!

40:10.141 --> 40:12.444
>> YEAH.

40:15.380 --> 40:17.048
>> WELL, SHIT.

40:17.048 --> 40:19.718
AIN'T THIS GRAND.

40:19.718 --> 40:22.087
ANYBODY HERE?

40:22.087 --> 40:24.790
>> LOOKIN' FOR US, CREEP?

40:24.790 --> 40:26.658
[ GROANING ]

40:26.658 --> 40:27.092
>> DO YOU THINK THIS

40:27.092 --> 40:27.993
IS FUCKING FUNNY,

40:27.993 --> 40:30.295
TRYING TO SCARE US LIKE THAT?

40:30.295 --> 40:31.663
WE'LL SHOW YOU.

40:31.663 --> 40:34.265
[ GRUNTING ]

40:34.265 --> 40:36.201
>> VIRG...

40:40.105 --> 40:42.173
[ GROANING ]

40:43.274 --> 40:53.985
[ MUSIC ]

40:53.985 --> 40:55.086
>> WE DID IT.

40:55.086 --> 40:55.987
>> YEAH!

40:55.987 --> 40:57.122
WE KILLED IT!

40:57.122 --> 40:58.323
>> HEY, HEY, HEY!

40:58.323 --> 40:59.991
GET BACK HERE!

40:59.991 --> 41:02.193
[ INDISTINCT YELLING ]

41:03.529 --> 41:04.696
>> SEE, TOLD YOU, MAN.

41:04.696 --> 41:05.263
REBECCA CAN TAKE CARE

41:05.263 --> 41:06.798
OF HERSELF.

41:06.798 --> 41:07.533
>> YEAH, I GUESS SO,

41:07.533 --> 41:08.534
BUT I REALLY THOUGHT

41:08.534 --> 41:10.068
THERE WERE TWO OF 'EM.

41:10.068 --> 41:11.803
>> I SHALL PROTECT YOU.

41:11.803 --> 41:14.105
>> MY HERO.

41:29.387 --> 41:31.189
>> STRANGE THINGS, JO.

41:31.189 --> 41:33.024
I DON'T LIKE IT.

41:33.024 --> 41:35.293
>> THINK IT'LL BE ALL RIGHT?

41:35.293 --> 41:36.194
>> WHO'S TO SAY?

41:36.194 --> 41:37.929
IT'S BEEN QUIET FOR YEARS.

41:37.929 --> 41:40.599
>> YEAH, WELL, CAN'T BE HELPED.

41:44.235 --> 41:46.137
BEST TO PREPARE, JUST IN CASE.

41:59.317 --> 41:59.785
>> ALL RIGHT,

41:59.785 --> 42:00.285
WE'LL TRY THAT AGAIN.

42:00.285 --> 42:01.119
YOU WANT YOU TO GO HIGH,

42:01.119 --> 42:01.920
AND I'LL GO LOW?

42:01.920 --> 42:03.054
OR YOU WANNA GO LOW?

42:03.054 --> 42:03.655
>> OH...

42:03.655 --> 42:06.057
I'LL-- I'LL TAKE THE HIGH ROAD.

42:06.057 --> 42:07.726
>> GOOD CHOICE.

42:07.726 --> 42:08.860
[singing] GLORY GLORY

42:08.860 --> 42:10.328
>> WAIT.

42:10.328 --> 42:12.831
MINE EYES HAVE SEEN THE COMING

42:12.831 --> 42:14.933
OF THE GLORY OF THE LORD

42:14.933 --> 42:15.601
>> I GUESS WE DON'T

42:15.601 --> 42:16.501
KNOW THE LYRICS, FATHER.

42:16.501 --> 42:17.736
>> WE DON'T KNOW THE LYRICS.

42:17.736 --> 42:21.339
AND SAINTS GO MARCHING IN

42:21.339 --> 42:25.276
GLORY GLORY HALLELUJAH

42:25.276 --> 42:29.214
GLORY GLORY HALLELUJAH

42:29.214 --> 42:32.618
GLORY GLORY HALLELUJAH

42:32.618 --> 42:35.687
HIS TRUTH IS MARCHING ON

42:35.687 --> 42:36.722
>> OH, THAT'S A WONDERFUL SONG.

42:36.722 --> 42:37.656
>> WELL DONE, WELL DONE.

42:37.656 --> 42:38.256
>> WONDERFUL SONG.

42:38.256 --> 42:39.024
>> I LOVE YOUR VOICE, FATHER.

42:39.024 --> 42:40.626
IT'S LIKE A CHORUS OF ANGELS.

42:40.626 --> 42:41.259
>> YEAH, I REALLY FELT

42:41.259 --> 42:43.094
THE SPIRIT ON THAT ONE.

42:45.731 --> 42:46.431
>> MAN, I STILL CAN'T SEE

42:46.431 --> 42:48.834
NOTHIN' OUTTA THESE MASKS, MAN.

42:48.834 --> 42:51.870
[ GRUNTING ]

42:51.870 --> 42:52.403
DAMN IT, WYATT,

42:52.403 --> 42:54.673
WE FOUND MORE ASPHALT, MAN.

42:54.673 --> 42:55.506
UNLESS THESE KIDS ARE CAMPIN'

42:55.506 --> 42:56.341
IN THE MIDDLE OF THE STREET,

42:56.341 --> 42:56.842
I DON'T THINK WE GOING

42:56.842 --> 42:58.877
THE RIGHT WAY!

42:58.877 --> 42:59.344
OH CRAP, THERE'S

42:59.344 --> 42:59.911
A CAR COMIN', MAN!

42:59.911 --> 43:00.746
WHAT ARE WE GONNA DO?

43:00.746 --> 43:04.115
GLORY GLORY HALLELUJAH

43:04.115 --> 43:05.483
GLORY GLORY HALLELUJAH

43:05.483 --> 43:05.951
THEY CAN'T SEE US

43:05.951 --> 43:07.485
LIKE THIS, MAN!

43:07.485 --> 43:08.353
HALLELUJAH

43:08.353 --> 43:09.220
>> DEAR GOD,

43:09.220 --> 43:10.922
WHAT IS THAT UP THERE?

43:10.922 --> 43:11.422
>> OH MY...

43:11.422 --> 43:12.457
>> YOU SEE THAT?

43:12.457 --> 43:13.324
>> IT'S HORRIBLE.

43:13.324 --> 43:14.459
[ CAR HORN HONKING ]

43:14.459 --> 43:17.028
>> COME ON, MAN!

43:17.028 --> 43:18.563
>> OH GOD, IT'S TERRIBLE!

43:18.563 --> 43:20.131
>> GO, GO, GO, GO!!!

43:20.131 --> 43:20.966
[ TIRES SQUEALING ]

43:20.966 --> 43:22.834
JESUS CHRIST, WHAT THE HELL?!

43:22.834 --> 43:25.003
OH MY GOD, JESUS CHRIST!

43:25.003 --> 43:25.536
>> LET'S GET THE FUCK

43:25.536 --> 43:26.504
OUT OF HERE!

43:26.504 --> 43:29.741
[ BANJO MUSIC ]

43:29.741 --> 43:32.210
[ POLICE RADIO CHATTER ]

43:33.344 --> 43:37.215
[ PHONE RINGING ]

43:37.215 --> 43:38.116
>> HELLO, GOOD EVENING,

43:38.116 --> 43:39.250
SHERIFF'S STATION.

43:39.250 --> 43:41.552
DEPUTY SHERIFF MORGAN SPEAKING.

43:41.552 --> 43:42.587
WHOA!

43:42.587 --> 43:44.923
WHOA, EASY.

43:44.923 --> 43:46.191
FATHER...

43:46.191 --> 43:47.693
FATHER ROTHSTEIN.

43:47.693 --> 43:49.961
SETTLE DOWN, WHAT--

43:53.431 --> 43:55.701
A WHAT?

43:55.701 --> 43:58.804
UH, REALLY?

43:58.804 --> 44:01.139
YOU DON'T SAY?

44:01.139 --> 44:03.241
AND IT'S A SCARECROW?

44:05.243 --> 44:06.244
OKAY.

44:06.244 --> 44:08.780
OKAY, UH--

44:08.780 --> 44:11.616
SURE, A SCARECROW.

44:11.616 --> 44:13.719
UH, YEAH.

44:13.719 --> 44:15.286
YOU KNOW, FATHER, ISN'T IT--

44:15.286 --> 44:16.587
ISN'T IT A SIN FOR

44:16.587 --> 44:18.189
A MAN OF THE CLOTH TO

44:18.189 --> 44:20.325
PARTICIPATE IN PRANKS ON PEOPLE?

44:22.393 --> 44:23.594
REALLY?

44:23.594 --> 44:25.731
OKAY.

44:25.731 --> 44:27.799
OKAY, SURE.

44:27.799 --> 44:28.633
WELL, DID THE SHERIFF

44:28.633 --> 44:30.401
PUT YOU UP TO THIS?

44:30.401 --> 44:32.437
I BET HE DID.

44:32.437 --> 44:34.005
YEAH, WELL HE'S NOT

44:34.005 --> 44:36.407
GONNA GET ME OVER AGAIN.

44:36.407 --> 44:39.310
OKAY, WHERE?

44:39.310 --> 44:40.211
OKAY, I'M HEADED THERE

44:40.211 --> 44:41.980
RIGHT NOW.

44:41.980 --> 44:44.149
RIGHT, RIGHT.

44:46.151 --> 44:48.519
MAN OH MAN.

44:59.430 --> 45:01.599
[ DOG BARKING ]

45:12.811 --> 45:13.611
>> BETTY, I SUSPECT

45:13.611 --> 45:15.881
THAT DOG HAS TO GO OUT.

45:15.881 --> 45:16.681
>> SOMETHIN' OUT THERE

45:16.681 --> 45:18.850
GOT HIM ALL RILED UP.

45:18.850 --> 45:21.820
[ GROWLING ]

45:21.820 --> 45:24.089
[ BARKING ]

45:26.324 --> 45:28.093
>> ALRIGHTY THEN.

45:31.863 --> 45:33.698
[ BARKING ]

45:33.698 --> 45:34.632
>> GO ON, NOW!

45:34.632 --> 45:35.901
COME ON, GIT!

45:35.901 --> 45:36.802
GIT!

45:36.802 --> 45:37.803
HA!

45:37.803 --> 45:42.073
[ BARKING CONTINUES ]

45:42.073 --> 45:43.809
[ WHIMPERING ]

45:43.809 --> 45:44.375
>> LITTLE FELLA

45:44.375 --> 45:46.711
SEEMS ALL RILED UP OUT THERE.

45:49.180 --> 45:50.315
I'D BEST GO CHECK.

45:50.315 --> 45:50.982
WE DON'T NEED ANOTHER

45:50.982 --> 45:52.517
SKUNK INCIDENT.

45:52.517 --> 45:53.718
>> OR WORSE.

45:53.718 --> 45:54.285
[ SCOFFING ]

45:54.285 --> 45:56.154
>> OR WORSE.

46:03.028 --> 46:06.331
[ GROWLING ]

46:06.331 --> 46:07.565
IT'S WORSE.

46:07.565 --> 46:08.399
[ LAUGHING ]

46:08.399 --> 46:08.934
>> I DON'T KNOW WHAT'S

46:08.934 --> 46:09.901
GOTTEN INTO YOU, WYATT,

46:09.901 --> 46:11.436
BUT THAT SURE WAS FUNNY, MAN.

46:11.436 --> 46:13.872
OH, JESUS.

46:13.872 --> 46:15.473
>> WHERE'S MY PISTOL?

46:15.473 --> 46:16.474
THERE'S SOMETHIN' OUT THERE.

46:16.474 --> 46:17.642
>> COME ON, MAN.

46:17.642 --> 46:19.277
COME ON.

46:24.449 --> 46:25.416
WYATT, YOU GOT A MEAN

46:25.416 --> 46:26.952
OL' STREAK IN YOU, MAN.

46:26.952 --> 46:28.253
[ GROWLING ]

46:28.253 --> 46:28.753
[ CHUCKLING ]

46:28.753 --> 46:29.921
OKAY, I KINDA FIGURED

46:29.921 --> 46:30.922
YOU'D SAY THAT.

46:30.922 --> 46:31.857
NOW CAN WE STOP FOOLIN' AROUND

46:31.857 --> 46:33.091
AND GO FIND THOSE KIDS?

46:33.091 --> 46:35.193
COME ON, MAN.

46:43.434 --> 46:45.136
>> HOW ABOUT OREOS?

46:45.136 --> 46:46.237
>> I LIKE THEM.

46:46.237 --> 46:49.174
>> HOW ABOUT BEING ONE?

46:49.174 --> 46:51.209
>> WHAT?

46:53.378 --> 46:57.148
[ PANTING ]

46:57.148 --> 46:58.884
>> OL' JOSEPHINE WAS RIGHT,

46:58.884 --> 47:01.319
NO GOOD CAN COME OF THIS.

47:01.319 --> 47:02.053
>> SCARECROW!

47:02.053 --> 47:03.121
>> WE'RE GONNA GET YA!

47:03.121 --> 47:03.989
[ LAUGHING ]

47:03.989 --> 47:05.490
>> OH, CHRIST ALL FRIDAY!

47:05.490 --> 47:07.092
>> COME OUT AND PLAY!

47:07.092 --> 47:09.294
[ BANJO MUSIC PLAYING ]

47:11.897 --> 47:14.365
[ POLICE RADIO CHATTER ]

47:20.906 --> 47:21.672
[ BELL RINGING ]

47:21.672 --> 47:22.607
>> SHERIFF, SHERIFF!

47:22.607 --> 47:23.341
YOU GOTTA GIVE ME A HAND

47:23.341 --> 47:25.010
ON SOMETHIN'.

47:25.010 --> 47:27.645
HEY, UH, NICE TO SEE YOU DEPUTY.

47:27.645 --> 47:28.313
>> HOW YA DOIN', BILL?

47:28.313 --> 47:28.779
>> HOW ARE YA?

47:28.779 --> 47:29.414
>> GOOD, GOOD.

47:29.414 --> 47:30.381
HOW'S IT GOIN'?

47:30.381 --> 47:32.150
>> I WAS WONDERIN' IF, POSSIBLY,

47:32.150 --> 47:33.051
UH, YOU COULD GET THE SHERIFF

47:33.051 --> 47:33.919
TO COME OUT OF THE BACK?

47:33.919 --> 47:34.920
I'M HAVIN' A SITUATION

47:34.920 --> 47:36.087
WITH MY DOG.

47:36.087 --> 47:36.988
>> YEAH, WHAT'S THE SITUATION

47:36.988 --> 47:38.489
WITH THE DOG?

47:38.489 --> 47:39.925
>> WELL, I'M SURE YOU CAN HANDLE

47:39.925 --> 47:41.326
REGULAR DOG SITUATIONS,

47:41.326 --> 47:42.027
BUT BELIEVE ME,

47:42.027 --> 47:42.961
THIS IS A--

47:42.961 --> 47:44.229
UNUSUAL DOG SITUATION,

47:44.229 --> 47:45.196
AND, UH--

47:45.196 --> 47:45.796
>> REALLY?

47:45.796 --> 47:46.531
>> WE'D JUST AS SOON HAVE

47:46.531 --> 47:47.532
THE SHERIFF'S EXPERTISE

47:47.532 --> 47:48.399
AND YEARS OF EXPERIENCE

47:48.399 --> 47:49.667
ON THE CASE.

47:49.667 --> 47:50.401
>> RIGHT.

47:50.401 --> 47:51.502
UH, HE'S NOT REACHABLE

47:51.502 --> 47:52.237
RIGHT NOW.

47:52.237 --> 47:53.071
I COULD HELP YOU OUT

47:53.071 --> 47:55.106
IF YOU NEED IT.

47:55.106 --> 47:56.474
>> YES, THAT WOULD BE WONDERFUL.

47:56.474 --> 47:57.608
BUT IF WE COULD PERHAPS

47:57.608 --> 47:59.077
HAVE THE SHERIFF, UH,

47:59.077 --> 48:00.311
CONSULTED BY PHONE?

48:00.311 --> 48:00.946
>> WELL, I CAN LEAVE HIM

48:00.946 --> 48:02.113
A MESSAGE, TELL HIM

48:02.113 --> 48:03.748
TO GET AHOLD OF YA.

48:03.748 --> 48:04.983
>> WELL, IS HE ON VACATION

48:04.983 --> 48:05.951
MUCH LONGER, DEPUTY?

48:05.951 --> 48:08.653
>> UH, A FEW MORE DAYS.

48:08.653 --> 48:10.288
>> I GUESS I'LL WAIT AT HOME

48:10.288 --> 48:11.389
FOR MY ANSWER, AND YOU COULD

48:11.389 --> 48:12.523
HAVE HIM, UH, CALL ME

48:12.523 --> 48:13.558
AT YOUR FIRST CONVENIENCE?

48:13.558 --> 48:14.225
>> OKAY.

48:14.225 --> 48:15.293
>> OKAY, THANK YOU, DEPUTY.

48:15.293 --> 48:15.860
>> THANK YOU.

48:15.860 --> 48:16.394
>> HAVE A GOOD DAY.

48:16.394 --> 48:17.095
>> YOU TOO.

48:17.095 --> 48:19.230
[ BELL RINGING ]

48:26.104 --> 48:27.538
>> GOOD NIGHT.

48:27.538 --> 48:29.674
>> GOOD NIGHT.

48:29.674 --> 48:32.377
>> AND SLEEP TIGHT.

48:32.377 --> 48:34.612
AND MAKE SURE YOU SLEEP.

48:42.420 --> 48:51.396
[ MUSIC ]

48:51.396 --> 48:52.463
>> TIMMY!

48:52.463 --> 48:56.201
TIMMY!

48:56.201 --> 48:56.801
>> WHAT?

48:56.801 --> 48:57.502
I WAS SLEEPIN'.

48:57.502 --> 48:59.470
MOM'LL GET MAD.

48:59.470 --> 49:01.006
>> TIMMY, I'M SCARED.

49:01.006 --> 49:01.606
>> OF WHAT?

49:01.606 --> 49:03.341
GO TO SEEP.

49:03.341 --> 49:04.675
>> THE SCARECROW.

49:04.675 --> 49:06.244
>> THERE'S NO SUCH THING.

49:06.244 --> 49:07.012
>> OH YEAH?

49:07.012 --> 49:09.014
LOOK.

49:09.014 --> 49:11.816
[ BOTH SCREAMING ]

49:11.816 --> 49:12.650
>> WYATT!

49:12.650 --> 49:13.418
WHAT IN THE SAM HILL

49:13.418 --> 49:14.885
ARE YOU DOIN' NOW, MAN?

49:14.885 --> 49:15.520
I SWEAR, WHAT HAS

49:15.520 --> 49:17.022
GOTTEN INTO YOU, DUDE?

49:17.022 --> 49:17.922
>> IT'S A SCARECROW,

49:17.922 --> 49:20.291
IT'S A SCARECROW AT THE WINDOW!

49:20.291 --> 49:21.192
>> GET YOUR GUN, DAD,

49:21.192 --> 49:22.693
AND BLAST IT!

49:22.693 --> 49:23.494
>> WE GOT TO GIT, WYATT!

49:23.494 --> 49:25.463
COME ON, MAN!

49:27.798 --> 49:28.299
WYATT, DO YOU KNOW

49:28.299 --> 49:29.067
WHAT GIT MEANS?

49:29.067 --> 49:31.336
COME ON!

49:37.142 --> 49:39.477
>> YOU SEE ANYTHING?

49:39.477 --> 49:40.545
>> NO.

49:40.545 --> 49:41.846
I'M GONNA GO CHECK.

49:41.846 --> 49:42.513
YOU LOCK THE DOOR AND HOLE UP

49:42.513 --> 49:43.281
WITH THE KIDS, OKAY?

49:43.281 --> 49:45.883
>> OKAY.

49:45.883 --> 49:48.053
CAREFUL, YOU DAMN FOOL.

49:50.655 --> 49:53.524
[ SHOTGUN RACKING ]

49:53.524 --> 49:55.060
>> JUST IN CASE.

49:55.060 --> 49:55.560
>> YOU KNOW THAT WON'T

49:55.560 --> 49:56.794
DO NO GOOD.

49:56.794 --> 49:59.164
EXCEPT MAKE IT MAD.

49:59.164 --> 50:00.598
>> WELL, JO, I'M JUST HOPIN'

50:00.598 --> 50:02.600
IT'S NOTHIN' BUT YOUR NERVES.

50:05.536 --> 50:05.936
YOU SHOULDN'T HAVE

50:05.936 --> 50:08.339
TOLD THAT STORY.

50:09.674 --> 50:11.976
JUST SAYIN'.

50:14.279 --> 50:15.080
>> EVERY TIME I GET TO SCHOOL,

50:15.080 --> 50:15.913
I TELL HIM HE HAS TO GO

50:15.913 --> 50:16.781
TO THE BATHROOM

50:16.781 --> 50:18.383
AND LICK THE TOILET.

50:18.383 --> 50:20.218
I EVEN TOLD HIM, "MY DAD'S

50:20.218 --> 50:21.552
THE SHERIFF, YOU HAVE TO

50:21.552 --> 50:23.188
DO WHAT I SAY."

50:23.188 --> 50:24.222
THERE'S REALLY NO OPTION.

50:24.222 --> 50:25.590
>> I TELL YOU WHAT!

50:25.590 --> 50:27.225
>> OH, I DON'T WANNA KNOW THAT!

50:27.225 --> 50:28.326
>> YEAH, I PANCAKED HIM.

50:28.326 --> 50:29.960
IT WAS-- IT WAS TERRIBLE, MAN.

50:29.960 --> 50:31.062
>> THAT'S GROSS.

50:31.062 --> 50:31.996
>> OH YEAH, WE DIDN'T KNOW WHAT

50:31.996 --> 50:33.264
TO DO WITH HIM, SO WE KINDA JUST

50:33.264 --> 50:34.532
THREW HIM OUT IN THE BACK,

50:34.532 --> 50:35.766
AND WE JUST-- YOU KNOW,

50:35.766 --> 50:37.335
JUST ANOTHER GOPHER IN THE YARD.

50:37.335 --> 50:39.070
[ CHUCKLING ]

50:39.070 --> 50:40.605
>> I-- I FULLY SUPPORT

50:40.605 --> 50:41.106
WHAT YOU TOLD US.

50:41.106 --> 50:42.006
>> EVAN!

50:42.006 --> 50:43.308
EVAN!

50:43.308 --> 50:44.575
EVAN!

50:44.575 --> 50:46.544
OKAY, YOUR MOM WAS TALKIN'

50:46.544 --> 50:48.413
TO MY MOM ABOUT HOW

50:48.413 --> 50:50.315
SHE WAS TALKING TO YOUR UNCLE--

50:50.315 --> 50:51.882
IT'S KINDA LIKE, MY GRANDPA,

50:51.882 --> 50:52.417
HE WAS TALKIN' TO

50:52.417 --> 50:53.851
THE CONVENIENCE STORE GUY,

50:53.851 --> 50:55.019
WHICH I THINK WAS TALKIN'--

50:55.019 --> 50:56.887
>> WELL GET ON WITH IT, NOW!

50:56.887 --> 50:57.788
>> THIS SCARECROW POPS

50:57.788 --> 50:59.290
OUTTA NOWHERE, AND SCARES

50:59.290 --> 51:00.725
YOUR BROTHER AND SISTER.

51:00.725 --> 51:02.460
>> MY BROTHER AND SISTER?

51:02.460 --> 51:04.262
>> WHAT ARE YOU GONNA DO?

51:04.262 --> 51:05.029
>> WE'RE GONNA GET

51:05.029 --> 51:06.131
THAT SUMBITCH!

51:06.131 --> 51:06.864
>> YEAH!

51:06.864 --> 51:07.432
LET'S GET 'UM!

51:07.432 --> 51:07.965
>> YEAH!!!

51:07.965 --> 51:10.368
>> COME ON!

51:13.871 --> 51:15.440
[ CAR ENGINE REVVING ]

51:15.440 --> 51:17.275
[ PANTING ]

51:19.610 --> 51:21.812
>> JUST GOTTA CATCH MY BREATH.

51:23.681 --> 51:24.449
I WAS NOT PREPARED FOR

51:24.449 --> 51:26.517
THE EXERTION TODAY.

51:26.517 --> 51:28.786
[ CAR APPROACHING ]

51:30.255 --> 51:32.423
[ HOOTING AND HOLLERING ]

51:33.858 --> 51:35.893
WHAT THE HELL IS GOIN' ON HERE?

51:35.893 --> 51:36.427
VIRG, WHEN I GET

51:36.427 --> 51:38.596
MY HANDS ON YOU...

51:42.600 --> 51:44.669
[ APPROACHING CAR STOPS ]

51:44.669 --> 51:47.071
[ INDISTINCT SHOUTING ]

51:53.411 --> 51:54.512
>> WAIT, DID YOU

51:54.512 --> 51:56.281
BRING IT THIS TIME?

51:56.281 --> 51:56.681
>> YEAH.

51:56.681 --> 51:57.448
>> NOT LIKE LAST TIME?

51:57.448 --> 51:58.983
>> YEAH.

51:58.983 --> 52:00.985
>> WELL, WHERE IS IT?

52:02.052 --> 52:04.622
>> SHIT, IT'S IN THE CAR.

52:04.622 --> 52:06.924
>> YOU'D BEST GO GET IT, THEN.

52:09.360 --> 52:10.795
AND MORE WINE, TOO.

52:10.795 --> 52:13.198
HURRY, BEFORE I CHANGE MY MIND.

52:16.401 --> 52:18.569
YOU'RE MINE NOW, YOU BIG DUMMY.

52:18.569 --> 52:19.404
[ GROWLING ]

52:19.404 --> 52:21.306
[ SCREAMING ]

52:21.306 --> 52:23.073
[ LAUGHING ]

52:23.073 --> 52:23.641
>> THAT WAS SOME

52:23.641 --> 52:25.210
FUNNY SHIT, WYATT!

52:25.210 --> 52:26.677
[ GROWLING ]

52:26.677 --> 52:27.545
>> WHAT THE HELL?

52:27.545 --> 52:28.045
I'LL GET YOU,

52:28.045 --> 52:29.814
YOU SON OF A BITCH!

52:29.814 --> 52:30.581
>> COME ON, JOE.

52:30.581 --> 52:32.217
I WANT TO GO HOME.

52:32.217 --> 52:32.617
>> DAMN IT.

52:32.617 --> 52:35.019
>> I WANT TO GO HOME NOW!

52:35.019 --> 52:36.821
>> IF I FIND THAT GUY...

52:36.821 --> 52:37.855
> OH MAN, YOU'RE PISSIN' OFF

52:37.855 --> 52:38.956
EVERYBODY TONIGHT.

52:38.956 --> 52:40.258
LET'S SKEDADDLE, MAN.

52:40.258 --> 52:42.560
[ CAR ENGINE STARTING ]

52:44.462 --> 52:59.444
[ MUSIC ]

53:00.745 --> 53:04.249
[ STICK DRAGGING ON GROUND ]

53:04.249 --> 53:06.351
>> COME ON, KELLY, KEEP UP.

53:06.351 --> 53:08.419
>> I'M GETTIN' KINDA BORED.

53:08.419 --> 53:09.954
AND TIRED.

53:09.954 --> 53:11.389
>> DO YOU WANNA GO BACK?

53:11.389 --> 53:14.992
DON'T YOU WANNA CATCH THIS GUY?

53:14.992 --> 53:16.261
THERE'S A HOUSE RIGHT THERE.

53:16.261 --> 53:16.627
WE'LL GO AND SEE

53:16.627 --> 53:18.329
IF THEY SAW ANYTHING.

53:18.329 --> 53:20.631
>> WHAT IF IT'S NOT A GUY?

53:22.700 --> 53:23.167
>> DO YOU MEAN,

53:23.167 --> 53:23.968
"WHAT IF IT'S NOT A GUY?"

53:23.968 --> 53:26.671
AS IN, IT'S AN ACTUAL SCARECROW?

53:26.671 --> 53:28.906
[ LAUGHING ]

53:31.809 --> 53:33.944
WE'LL STILL BEAT ITS ASS.

53:33.944 --> 53:34.579
>> HEY!

53:34.579 --> 53:36.013
WHO GOES THERE?

53:36.013 --> 53:37.282
WHO ARE YOU?

53:37.282 --> 53:39.284
I HAVE A GUN AND I WILL USE IT.

53:39.284 --> 53:39.784
>> YEAH?

53:39.784 --> 53:40.418
WELL I HAVE THIS STICK,

53:40.418 --> 53:41.352
AND I'LL KICK YOUR ASS!

53:41.352 --> 53:42.287
>> DUDE, WAIT.

53:42.287 --> 53:43.488
HI, I'M-I'M KELLY,

53:43.488 --> 53:44.489
AND THIS IS REBECCA.

53:44.489 --> 53:46.424
WE-- WE'RE JUST CAMPIN'

53:46.424 --> 53:48.459
WITH SOME FRIENDS, AND--

53:48.459 --> 53:49.894
WHAT WE ASSUME WAS A DUDE

53:49.894 --> 53:50.861
DRESSED AS A SCARECROW

53:50.861 --> 53:52.430
CAME TO TERRORIZE US.

53:52.430 --> 53:53.431
WE BEAT HIM UP, AND NOW

53:53.431 --> 53:54.765
WE'RE JUST CHASIN' HIM.

53:54.765 --> 53:55.800
MY FRIEND WILL KICK YOUR ASS

53:55.800 --> 53:57.368
IF YOU TRY TO HURT US.

53:57.368 --> 53:58.135
>> ALL RIGHT, ALL RIGHT,

53:58.135 --> 53:59.404
FAIR ENOUGH.

53:59.404 --> 54:00.971
I-- I TOO AM CHASING A MAN

54:00.971 --> 54:03.040
DRESSED AS A SCARECROW.

54:03.040 --> 54:04.074
HE SCARED THE BEJEEZUS

54:04.074 --> 54:05.643
OUT OF MY LITTLE ONES.

54:05.643 --> 54:06.143
WE DON'T NEED THIS KIND

54:06.143 --> 54:08.112
OF CRAP AROUND HERE.

54:08.112 --> 54:09.314
[ SCREAMING ]

54:09.314 --> 54:11.048
>> WHAT THE HELL?

54:11.048 --> 54:11.616
>> I'LL GET YOU,

54:11.616 --> 54:12.683
YOU SON OF A BITCH!

54:12.683 --> 54:14.385
>> WE GOTTA GO HELP.

54:14.385 --> 54:15.520
>> WELL, HOLD ON NOW.

54:15.520 --> 54:16.687
WE SHOULD STICK TOGETHER.

54:16.687 --> 54:17.655
YOU KNOW, FOR SAFETY IN NUMBERS

54:17.655 --> 54:19.056
AND EVERYTHING.

54:19.056 --> 54:19.990
>> WHAT, ARE YOU SCARED TOO?

54:19.990 --> 54:20.791
IT'S JUST A GUY IN A COSTUME,

54:20.791 --> 54:22.493
RIGHT?

54:22.493 --> 54:24.695
>> OH LORD, I HOPE SO.

54:24.695 --> 54:25.863
>> THIS WHOLE SCARECROW THING

54:25.863 --> 54:28.833
IS JUST LEGEND, RIGHT?

54:28.833 --> 54:30.200
>> WELL, I DUNNO, IT'S--

54:30.200 --> 54:31.001
YEAH, IT'S--

54:31.001 --> 54:32.169
IT'S PROBABLY JUST A--

54:32.169 --> 54:34.905
A MAN IN A MASK OR SOMETHIN'.

54:34.905 --> 54:35.506
>> WHY DIDN'T HE

54:35.506 --> 54:36.907
ANSWER MY QUESTION?

54:36.907 --> 54:38.976
>> COME ON, LET'S GO!

54:40.978 --> 54:43.013
>> COME ON.

54:45.650 --> 54:47.752
[ PHONE RINGING ]

54:51.088 --> 54:52.923
>> SHERIFF'S OFFICE.

54:52.923 --> 54:55.460
WHAT?

54:55.460 --> 54:57.695
A SCARECROW?

54:57.695 --> 54:58.496
I'VE HEARD THIS.

54:58.496 --> 55:00.064
IS THIS-- IS THIS A JOKE?

55:00.064 --> 55:01.366
[ PHONE RINGING ]

55:01.366 --> 55:03.033
HOLD, PLEASE.

55:03.033 --> 55:05.570
SHERIFF'S OFFICE.

55:05.570 --> 55:08.639
YOU GOTTA BE KIDDING ME.

55:08.639 --> 55:09.907
OKAY, OKAY.

55:09.907 --> 55:11.376
[ PHONE RINGING ]

55:11.376 --> 55:12.643
HOLD, PLEASE.

55:12.643 --> 55:15.713
SHERIFF'S OFFICE.

55:15.713 --> 55:16.447
SERIOUSLY?!

55:16.447 --> 55:17.615
[ PHONE RINGING ]

55:17.615 --> 55:18.816
OKAY, HOLD, PLEASE.

55:18.816 --> 55:21.151
SHERIFF'S OFFICE.

55:21.151 --> 55:23.187
WHERE?

55:23.187 --> 55:25.556
WITH WHO?

55:25.556 --> 55:28.793
YOUR GIRLFRIEND, DOING WHAT?

55:28.793 --> 55:29.994
WITH A SCARECROW?

55:29.994 --> 55:31.529
[ PHONE RINGING ]

55:31.529 --> 55:32.563
OKAY, HOLD, PLEASE.

55:32.563 --> 55:34.699
SHERIFF'S OFFICE.

55:34.699 --> 55:36.767
HA, HA, HA, HA, FUNNY!

55:36.767 --> 55:38.703
FUNNY, I GET-- OKAY.

55:38.703 --> 55:41.005
BYE.

55:41.005 --> 55:41.672
>> I DUNNO WHAT THE HELL

55:41.672 --> 55:42.973
THOSE GUYS ARE UP TO.

55:42.973 --> 55:43.574
>> I HOPE WE NEVER

55:43.574 --> 55:44.709
SEE THEM AGAIN.

55:44.709 --> 55:45.410
OH MY GOD, JOE!

55:45.410 --> 55:46.477
THERE HE IS!

55:46.477 --> 55:47.778
>> WHAT THE HELL?

55:47.778 --> 55:49.780
>> AHH!

55:52.182 --> 55:53.484
>> HEY, 'SCUSE ME, PARTNER.

55:53.484 --> 55:54.719
>> YOU SON OF A BITCH!

55:54.719 --> 55:55.252
I'M GONNA WHOOP YOUR ASS!

55:55.252 --> 55:56.787
>> WHOA-WHOA-WHOA-WHOA!

55:56.787 --> 55:58.656
> JOE, GET BACK HERE!

55:58.656 --> 55:59.590
JOE!

55:59.590 --> 56:01.726
I'M SCARED!

56:03.928 --> 56:07.832
[ PANTING ]

56:07.832 --> 56:09.299
>> VIRG, OL' BOY,

56:09.299 --> 56:11.869
I GET THE DISTINCT IMPRESSION

56:11.869 --> 56:14.038
YOU WERE BEHIND THIS SOMEHOWS.

56:16.040 --> 56:16.674
[ ENGINE REVVING ]

56:16.674 --> 56:18.275
>> GET THAT SUMBITCH!

56:18.275 --> 56:19.810
[ HOOTING AND HOLLERING ]

56:19.810 --> 56:22.046
>> AW, HELL.

56:22.046 --> 56:23.881
>> YEAH, THERE HE IS!

56:28.953 --> 56:29.520
>> ALL RIGHT, WYATT,

56:29.520 --> 56:30.921
WHAT YOU THINK, MAN?

56:30.921 --> 56:32.457
SHOULD WE GO THAT WAY,

56:32.457 --> 56:35.292
OR THAT WAY?

56:35.292 --> 56:36.461
LET ME GUESS...

56:36.461 --> 56:38.062
"MMRGH!"

56:38.062 --> 56:39.229
[ GROWLING ]

56:39.229 --> 56:40.330
YEP, ALL RIGHT.

56:40.330 --> 56:42.533
COME ON.

56:51.041 --> 56:52.710
>> WATCH IT, YOU ASSHOLE!

56:52.710 --> 56:54.512
[ GROWLING ]

56:54.512 --> 56:55.913
>> HOLY CRAP, THAT WAS CLOSE!

56:55.913 --> 56:56.781
YOU OKAY, BUDDY?

56:56.781 --> 56:57.515
[ LAUGHING ]

56:57.515 --> 56:58.282
[ GROWLING ]

56:58.282 --> 56:59.484
OW, OKAY!

56:59.484 --> 57:00.818
OKAY MAN, BAD IDEA.

57:00.818 --> 57:01.619
GAME OVER, RIGHT?

57:01.619 --> 57:02.853
LET'S-- LET'S JUST

57:02.853 --> 57:04.088
GO BACK TO JOSEPHINE'S.

57:04.088 --> 57:05.322
MAYBE WE CAN GET LAST CALL,

57:05.322 --> 57:06.757
RIGHT?

57:06.757 --> 57:08.025
[ GROWLING ]

57:08.025 --> 57:08.726
KINDA FIGURED YOU'D

57:08.726 --> 57:09.594
SAY THAT, OL' BOY.

57:09.594 --> 57:11.762
COME ON, MAN.

57:16.567 --> 57:18.836
[ POLICE RADIO CHATTER ]

57:27.778 --> 57:28.513
[ BELL RINGING ]

57:28.513 --> 57:30.014
>> SHERIFF, THERE'S A MOB

57:30.014 --> 57:31.882
CONGREGATING-- OH, SHIT.

57:31.882 --> 57:32.349
>> OH, HEY BURT.

57:32.349 --> 57:33.217
HOW YOU DOIN'?

57:33.217 --> 57:34.084
>> I'M DOIN' VERY WELL.

57:34.084 --> 57:35.152
HOW ARE YOU TODAY?

57:35.152 --> 57:35.820
>> I'M-- I'M GREAT.

57:35.820 --> 57:36.954
HOW CAN I HELP YA?

57:36.954 --> 57:38.422
>> IS THE SHERIFF AROUND?

57:38.422 --> 57:40.424
>> I'M ACTING SHERIFF TONIGHT.

57:40.424 --> 57:41.191
>> WELL, THAT'S MIGHTY CUTE

57:41.191 --> 57:42.527
OF YOU, BUT WE'RE GONNA NEED

57:42.527 --> 57:43.393
THE SHERIFF ON THIS ONE.

57:43.393 --> 57:44.729
THERE'S A MOB GATHERING JUST

57:44.729 --> 57:45.696
OUTSIDE OF THIS BUILDING.

57:45.696 --> 57:46.330
IT'S, LIKE, A LARGE

57:46.330 --> 57:47.197
GROUP OF PEOPLE.

57:47.197 --> 57:48.265
>> OKAY, WELL, THE SHERIFF

57:48.265 --> 57:49.534
ISN'T HERE RIGHT NOW.

57:49.534 --> 57:50.568
I CAN HELP.

57:50.568 --> 57:51.769
>> WELL, I DON'T KNOW EXACTLY

57:51.769 --> 57:52.637
HOW TO EXPLAIN IT, BUT THERE IS

57:52.637 --> 57:54.672
A-- THERE IS A, UH--

57:54.672 --> 57:57.842
>> LET ME GUESS, A SCARECROW.

57:57.842 --> 57:58.342
>> WELL, YES.

57:58.342 --> 57:58.976
IT'S EITHER THAT, OR AN

57:58.976 --> 58:00.377
AMBULATORY SACK OF HAY

58:00.377 --> 58:01.679
MADE BY A WIZARD.

58:01.679 --> 58:02.547
NOW WOULD YOU GO

58:02.547 --> 58:03.681
GET YOUR BELT ON?

58:03.681 --> 58:05.115
YOU'RE JUST GONNA HAVE TO DO.

58:05.115 --> 58:05.750
>> ALL RIGHT,

58:05.750 --> 58:06.283
I'LL BE RIGHT BACK.

58:06.283 --> 58:06.684
[ PHONE RINGING ]

58:06.684 --> 58:07.184
>> ALL RIGHT.

58:07.184 --> 58:07.785
GO CALL YOUR MOM,

58:07.785 --> 58:09.787
TELL HER YOU MIGHT BE LATE.

58:15.059 --> 58:17.427
AH, YESSS!

58:17.427 --> 58:19.363
ALL RIGHT.

58:19.363 --> 58:21.231
[ BELL RINGING ]

58:23.000 --> 58:25.135
[ PHONE RINGING ]

58:30.174 --> 58:31.742
>> HOW YOU DOIN' TODAY?

58:31.742 --> 58:32.743
SHERIFF.

58:32.743 --> 58:34.712
I'M THE DEPUTY SHERIFF.

58:34.712 --> 58:35.880
[ PHONE CONTINUES RINGING ]

58:35.880 --> 58:37.782
SHERIFF DEPUTY MORGAN...

58:37.782 --> 58:40.417
SPEAKING.

58:40.417 --> 58:42.620
IS THERE A PROBLEM?

58:42.620 --> 58:43.954
NO THAT'S NOT...

58:43.954 --> 58:47.592
IS THERE A PROBLEM?

58:47.592 --> 58:48.759
TOO AGGRESSIVE.

58:48.759 --> 58:49.727
[ RINGING CONTINUES ]

58:49.727 --> 58:50.595
IS THERE A WAY

58:50.595 --> 58:53.130
WE CAN RESOLVE THIS?

58:53.130 --> 58:54.699
THERE'S TWO WAYS THAT

58:54.699 --> 58:56.901
WE COULD FIGURE THIS OUT.

58:56.901 --> 58:59.604
UH, A FRIENDLY MEETING,

58:59.604 --> 59:01.806
SOMEWHERE WITH FOOD,

59:01.806 --> 59:03.741
OR, UH--

59:03.741 --> 59:06.043
YOU GO TO JAIL.

59:09.747 --> 59:12.683
[ ENGINE REVVING ]

59:12.683 --> 59:16.086
[ INDISTINCT SHOUTING ]

59:16.086 --> 59:16.887
>> WHOLE DAMN TOWN'S

59:16.887 --> 59:19.624
IN AN UPROAR.

59:19.624 --> 59:20.625
VIRGIL, THIS IS

59:20.625 --> 59:23.460
A DUMB ASS SHITTIN' IDEA.

59:23.460 --> 59:24.094
YOU'RE STUPID EVEN

59:24.094 --> 59:26.631
FOR INBRED STANDARDS.

59:26.631 --> 59:29.066
DAMN, UGH!

59:29.066 --> 59:30.668
[ SIGHING ]

59:30.668 --> 59:31.902
SCREW IT,

59:31.902 --> 59:34.004
I'M GONNA GET ME A BEER.

59:41.812 --> 59:43.313
>> NOW WE GOT TO ALL CALM DOWN,

59:43.313 --> 59:44.815
AND NOT BE STUPID.

59:44.815 --> 59:45.783
OR MORE STUPID.

59:45.783 --> 59:47.017
>> HE'S A DAMN MENACE, SHERIFF!

59:47.017 --> 59:48.318
[ COLLECTIVE SHOUTING ]

59:48.318 --> 59:49.519
>> I UNDERSTAND, I UNDERSTAND.

59:49.519 --> 59:50.855
DOES ANYBODY HAVE ANY IDEA

59:50.855 --> 59:53.557
WHO COULD BE BEHIND THIS?

59:53.557 --> 59:54.124
>> I THINK IT WAS A COUPLE

59:54.124 --> 59:54.659
OF GUYS WE SAW DOWN

